==Most prominent summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most prominent summits}}
Of the most prominent summits of New Mexico, [[Sierra Blanca (New Mexico)|Sierra Blanca Peak]] is an [[ultra-prominent summit]] with more than {{convert|1500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence and 12 peaks exceed {{convert|1000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.
{{clear}}
